  A[🎨 User edits]<-->B[📝 Recording]
  B-->C[💾 Export\nrecording file]
  C-->D[🔄 New Blender\nproject + Add-on]
  D-->E[🎬 Render\ntimelapse video]
  
  style A fill:#1a1a1a,color:#fff,stroke:#333
  style B fill:#1a1a1a,color:#fff,stroke:#333
