# Feasibility: Architecture

<div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr] gap-2 items-center mt-4">

<div class="p-3 rounded border border-gray/20">
  <div class="font-bold text-sm">Fusion Engine</div>
  <div class="text-xs text-muted mt-1">
    Fuse multiple event sources into<br/>a unified action timeline
  </div>
</div>

<div class="text-xl text-muted"><span class="i-carbon:arrow-right" /></div>

<div class="p-3 rounded border border-gray/20">
  <div class="font-bold text-sm">Timeline → Frames</div>
  <div class="text-xs text-muted mt-1">
    Each action → one rendered frame<br/>Camera: interpolated from viewport
  </div>
</div>

</div>

<div class="mt-6 p-3 rounded bg-gray/5 text-sm">

**Challenge:** No single `operator_pre/post` callback exists  
→ Must fuse: `OP_POLL` + `DEPSGRAPH` + `SNAPSHOT` + `VIEW_TIMER`

**Script executions** detectable, but non-`bpy.ops` steps inside scripts only visible as deltas (before/after comparison)

</div>

