  <div class="font-bold text-purple">Stretch Goals</div>
  <ul class="text-xs mt-2 text-muted">
    <li>Undo-tree filtering</li>
    <li>Sculpt mode recording</li>
    <li>Custom frame timing</li>
    <li>Full Cycles/Eevee render support</li>
    <li>Vertex/edge visualization overlays</li>
  </ul>
</div>

